{"tid":2095101,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"《基本法》要怎樣擁護？ - 古德明","createTime":"2020-07-05T07:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T07:59:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"77674ff179030cad4bbeff6c8c841cdffa1628d6","tid":2095101,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:59:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20200705/20949683/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200705%2F20949683%2F&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj32yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=1bc18b02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200705%2F20949683%2F&h=599458e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20200705/20949683/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》要怎樣擁護？ - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200705/large/1593848253_4fb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200705%2Flarge%2F1593848253_4fb9.jpg&h=763e4ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新香港立法會行當改選，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n新香港高官言論，真是無奇不有。<br />\n<br />\n按《香港基本法》第五十二條分明規定：「行政長官如因立法會拒絕通過財政預算案或其他重要法案而解散立法會，重選的立法會繼續拒絕通過所爭議的原案，則行政長官必須辭職。」然則運用否決權迫使「行政長官」辭職，本是《基本法》提出的手段，假如這等於「癱瘓立法會甚至整個香港」，則《基本法》條文是不是也有「不能算是效忠於香港」者？遵從《基本法》行事，什麼情況之下才算效忠於香港以及黨國，什麼情況之下則算不效忠，是不是隨長官好惡而定？立法會參選人現在須聲明擁護《基本法》，但原來擁護《基本法》第五十二條竟然連參選資格都可能喪失。<br />\n<br />\n曾國衞任入境事務處長期間，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n現在刑賞都隨長官好惡而定。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"}]}